---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getPath } from '../../utils/pathUtils';
---

<BaseLayout title="Work — Digital Transformation at Scale" currentPage="work">
    <div class="page-container">
        <h1>Work — Digital Transformation at Scale</h1>
        
        <p>
            Across four decades, the work has evolved from silicon-layer innovation to cloud-scale 
            systems to sustainable AI. What remains constant: simplifying complexity, building bridges 
            across organizations, and moving technology from potential to impact.
        </p>

        <section class="content-categories">
            <div class="category-card">
                <h2><a href={getPath('/work/telecom')}>Telecommunications Era (1980s-90s)</a></h2>
                <p>
                    Silicon-layer innovation, telecommunications infrastructure, early digital systems, 
                    and the foundations of modern connectivity. Building under constraints of limited 
                    bandwidth, nascent networks, and emerging standards.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="category-card">
                <h2><a href={getPath('/work/enterprise')}>Enterprise & Cloud Era (2000s-2010s)</a></h2>
                <p>
                    Microsoft platforms, digital analytics at global scale, enterprise transformation, 
                    and cloud-based systems architecture. Leading cross-functional teams through the 
                    shift from on-premise to cloud infrastructure.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="category-card">
                <h2><a href={getPath('/work/sustainable-ai')}>Sustainable AI Era (2020s)</a></h2>
                <p>
                    Climate-resilient AI, sustainable technology innovation, NITK AI Centre of Excellence, 
                    and regenerative systems design. Building AI that serves humanity and the planet 
                    without compromising future generations.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
